*************Installation for linux************************ 

To install kannada tex run shell script install.sh

To uninstall kannada tex run shell script uninstall.sh

***********************************************************

*************Installation for windows**********************

To install kannada TeX for windows run install.bat batch file.

To uninstall kannada tex run uninstall.bat batchfile.

***********************************************************

*********************USAGE*********************************

include \usepackage{kanlel} to activate kannada as default

manual for kannadatex is manual.pdf and one example file is udaya.tex.

